data.title: 1.3.6.1.4.1 - IANA-registered Private Enterprises
data.text:
The official assignments under this OID are stored in the IANA file "enterprise-numbers".

These numbers are used, among other things, for defining private SNMP MIBs.

In order to get your own number, use the IANA application form, and a new number will be emailed to you in a matter of days. (Register it here if you want to - but registering here will NOT assign the number at IANA!)

See also the OID Repository website reference for 1.3.6.1.4.1
